reviews.content:
I watched this to complete the Oscar Highlight Films List for 2012. Based on a movie poster or a one sentence description, I never would have watched this film. So, needless to say, I was amazed at how deeply moving this film turned out to be. The 165 minutes and years of storyline fly by and the viewer is left emotionally exhausted, but satisfied. There were no loose ends here. Before watching, be prepared for some depressing and difficult moments. This film is not for everyone and is not for everyday, but I'm glad I gave it a chance at a time where I could enjoy it.RealReview Posting Scoring Criteria:
